{"tid":477861,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"臨別AKB　渡邊麻友最後細碟首日銷量破百萬","createTime":"2017-11-23T12:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T00:35:39.000Z","uid":3806,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1a8b3b64df32adeb2f5801be0a5c8d4c548c57","tid":477861,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171123/photo/bkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001_01p.jpg?20171123173819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20171123173819&h=87e3a99c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渡邊麻友離開AKB前的最後擔正細碟《11月的Anklet》，首日銷量有104萬張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本偶像女團AKB48的23歲元祖級成員渡邊麻友，將於今年底正式離隊，結束長達10年的AKB生涯。由麻友最後擔正的AKB細碟《11月的Anklet》於昨日面世，首日銷量有104萬張，為麻友的偶像生涯完美句號。離隊前，麻友與隊友柏木由紀合演的旅遊節目將於下周三播出，兩人難得出走温泉旅行，更於節目中互訴心事。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，隨着AKB人氣成員相繼離隊，近日傳出AKB有意邀請「天使面」偶像橋本環奈以外援身份加盟拯救人氣。不過，外界擔心橋本客串擔任AKB成員，只會搶去組合焦點，令AKB進一步淪為陪襯品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171123/photo/bkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001_02b.jpg?20171123173819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20171123173819&h=33195511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻友將於今年內離隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171123/photo/bkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001_03b.jpg?20171123173819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20171123173819&h=b23c3036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻友（左）臨別前，與隊友柏木由紀演出旅遊節目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171123/photo/bkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001_04b.jpg?20171123173819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20171123173819&h=83240741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「天使面」偶像橋本環奈傳獲邀以外援身份，加盟AKB。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171123/bkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171123%2Fbkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001.html&d=Vj677ZQh3BTuz5Y4znqgEL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ebdd4b65\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171123/bkn-20171123161224096-1123_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6d2233e29bc8cf661de0757c921fe0535bd94293","tid":477861,"uid":90,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/trollpasta/images/b/b9/Chicken_sombrero.gif/revision/latest?cb=20150813060711\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Ftrollpasta%2Fimages%2Fb%2Fb9%2FChicken_sombrero.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20150813060711&h=7e70042b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"933399b604608b98497a9f5f4238b503cf162002","tid":477861,"uid":14965,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人買晒來做鬧鐘<br />\n<br />\n一到朝早就咯咯咯咯"},{"pid":"82f36dbd8ca7df2823a58789997081a6dc0cf7ac","tid":477861,"uid":3806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人買晒來做鬧鐘<br />\n<br />\n一到朝早就咯咯咯咯</blockquote><br />\n𨳒你老母親節"},{"pid":"af2544bf58c84b9c584c7fe22c0ec504b1f7556f","tid":477861,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11